{
  "stem": "13471.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And here's the letter-- I mean, here's the Navy's regulations, and here are my-- my backup statistics on this and so forth.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he says, oh, hell, Al, he says, you write the letter, I'll sign it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I became a commander in April of '46, I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then-- then to my astonishment and pleasure, in-- in August of '46, I got a confirmation from the Navy saying that was a temporary promotion to commander.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Your temporary promotion has now been made permanent because you have served satisfactorily within this new rank.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, see, I was running my own career.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But no longer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You can't do that anymore in the Navy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have a-- a diagram over there--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well, you walk in, and the body of the court-- let's say you walk in the main door.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The body of the court was on the level that you walked in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To your right, as you walked in, there were seats like in a movie theater, sort of going up in the back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These were the spectators.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then to the left, there would be a row of tables for the prosecutors, a separate table for each prosecutor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The table might seat anywhere from six to-- or from two to three to six or eight lawyers, depending on what was going on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then on the far side of the room, elevated, were the judges, eight of them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Four for each country.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was on the far side.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then to the-- to the left, as you walked in, so around to your left, would be the defendants in the dock.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were 21 of them, I think it was, or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
